page.title: 01INTRODUCTION
page.content:
LAND ****
This block of squares is mostly wood and land. There are no shops or schools. There is about 8 or 9 farms at the most. So the rest of the land is fields. Also there is dissused quarries. There are reservoirs which are covered with soil. There is not much to do in the country but round the coast there are towns and villages which have castles and caves to look at. If you took the A92 road, this takes you to the villages. We try to keep Fife as tidy as we can for tourists to recommend our country. We hope you like the sights you see on your travels.
